{
  "chapter": "083",
  "title": "鲁仲连邹阳列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "鲁仲连其人",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁仲连</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国人。"
    },
    "1.2": {
      "title": "好奇策",
      "text": "他喜好奇伟俶傥的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">画策</span>，而不肯仕宦任职，喜欢保持高尚的节操。"
    },
    "1.3": {
      "title": "游于赵",
      "text": "曾游历于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "2.1": {
      "title": "秦破长平围邯郸",
      "text": "在<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">赵孝成王时</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">秦王（秦昭王）</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>的军队前后<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十馀</span>万人，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵随即东进<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>。"
    },
    "2.2": {
      "title": "诸侯救兵不敢击秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵孝成王\">赵王（赵孝成王）</span>恐惧，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的救兵没有人敢<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军。"
    },
    "2.3": {
      "title": "晋鄙畏秦止荡阴",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏安釐王</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>救援<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，畏惧<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，停留在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荡阴</span>不进。"
    },
    "2.4": {
      "title": "新垣衍献尊秦帝之策",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏安釐王\">魏王（魏安釐王）</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">客将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>潜入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，通过<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵孝成王\">赵王（赵孝成王）</span>说： \"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国之所以急于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，是因为从前与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span>争强为帝，不久之后又双双归复帝号；如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国已日渐衰弱，方今唯有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>雄踞<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，此次未必是贪图<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，其本意是想再次求为帝。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国如果确能派使者尊奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>为帝，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国一定会高兴，撤兵而去。\""
    },
    "2.5": {
      "title": "平原君犹预",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>犹豫不决。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "3.1": {
      "title": "鲁连见平原君",
      "text": "此时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁仲连</span>恰巧游历到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，适逢<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国将要让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国尊<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>为帝，便去见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>说： \"事情将怎么办？\""
    },
    "3.2": {
      "title": "平原君述困境",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>说： \"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>怎敢再言事！先前在国外丢失了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十万之众</span>，现在又在国内被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>而不能解围。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏安釐王\">魏王（魏安釐王）</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">客将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国尊<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>为帝，现在那人就在这里。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>怎敢再言事！\""
    },
    "3.3": {
      "title": "鲁连责平原君",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁仲连</span>说： \"我原以为您是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的贤<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>，今天才知道您不是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的贤<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国客人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>在哪里？我替您责备他，让他回去。\""
    },
    "3.4": {
      "title": "平原君允为介绍",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>说： \"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>请求替您介绍，与他相见。\""
    },
    "3.5": {
      "title": "平原君见新垣衍",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>于是见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>说： \"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东国</span>有位<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁仲连</span>先生，现在此地，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>请求为介绍，让他与将军相交。\""
    },
    "3.6": {
      "title": "新垣衍辞见",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>说： \"我听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁仲连</span>先生是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国的高<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：新垣衍\">衍（新垣衍）</span>是做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>的，有使命在身，我不愿见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁仲连</span>先生。\""
    },
    "3.7": {
      "title": "平原君已泄",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>说： \"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>已经把消息泄露了。\""
    },
    "3.8": {
      "title": "新垣衍许诺",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>于是答应了。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "4.1": {
      "title": "鲁连见新垣衍无言",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>见到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>却不说话。"
    },
    "4.2": {
      "title": "新垣衍问意",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>说： \"我看留在这<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>城之中的人，都是有求于<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>的人；现在我看先生的容貌，不像是有求于<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>的人，为何久居此<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>城之中而不离去？\""
    },
    "4.3": {
      "title": "鲁连斥秦弃礼义",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁仲连</span>说： \"世人以为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲍焦</span>没有大度气量而死，这都是错误的。众人不了解他，就以为他是为一己之身而死。那<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，是抛弃<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼义</span>而崇尚首级战功的国家，以权术驱使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，以奴役之法对待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众。它一旦肆无忌惮地称帝，进而在<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>施行政令，那么<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">连（鲁仲连）</span>唯有蹈<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东海</span>而死，我不忍心做它的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>。我所以要见将军，是想帮助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。\""
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "5.1": {
      "title": "新垣衍问如何助",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>说： \"先生将怎样帮助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>？\""
    },
    "5.2": {
      "title": "鲁连欲使梁燕助",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>说： \"我将使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>和<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>帮助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>本来就会帮助。\""
    },
    "5.3": {
      "title": "新垣衍问梁",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>说： \"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国方面，我姑且听从；至于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国，则我是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>国人，先生怎能使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>帮助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>呢？\""
    },
    "5.4": {
      "title": "鲁连言梁未睹秦帝之害",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>说： \"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>只是没有看到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>称帝的祸害罢了。若使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>看到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>称帝的祸害，必定会帮助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。\""
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "6.1": {
      "title": "新垣衍问秦帝之害",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>说： \"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>称帝的祸害如何？\""
    },
    "6.2": {
      "title": "鲁连举齐威王朝周之辱",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>说： \"从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐威王</span>曾施行<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁义</span>，率<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>去<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">朝</span>见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>贫困且势微，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>没人去朝见，只有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国去朝见。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周烈王</span>崩，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国晚到，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>发怒，向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>发讣说：'天崩地坼，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>下席寝苫。东方藩属之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田婴齐</span>因晚到，应该斩首。'<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐威王</span>勃然大怒说：'叱嗟！你<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲是婢女罢了！'最终成为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的笑话。所以他在位时<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">朝</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>，他死后又被叱骂，确实是不忍受他的要求。那<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>本来就是这样，他们的行为无足惊怪。\""
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "7.1": {
      "title": "新垣衍以仆为喻",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>说： \"先生难道没见过奴仆吗？<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十人</span>跟从<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>，难道是力气不<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">胜</span>过他、智力不如他吗？是畏惧他啊。\""
    },
    "7.2": {
      "title": "鲁连反诘",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁仲连</span>说： \"呜呼！<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>比于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>就像奴仆吗？\""
    },
    "7.3": {
      "title": "新垣衍肯认",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>说： \"是的。\""
    },
    "7.4": {
      "title": "鲁连言使秦烹梁王",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁仲连</span>说： \"我将要使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">秦王（秦昭王）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">烹</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">醢</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁王</span>。\""
    },
    "7.5": {
      "title": "新垣衍怏然",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>不高兴，说： \"噫嘻，先生的话太过分了！先生又怎能使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">秦王（秦昭王）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">烹</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">醢</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁王</span>？\""
    },
    "7.6": {
      "title": "鲁连论纣三公及齐湣王之辱",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁仲连</span>说： \"当然，我将说明。从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">九侯</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鄂侯</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周文王\">文王（周文王）</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">九侯</span>有女儿貌美，进献给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>认为她丑陋，就把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">九侯</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">醢</span>为肉酱。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鄂侯</span>极力争辩，言辞激烈，所以被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">脯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鄂侯</span>做成肉干。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周文王\">文王（周文王）</span>听说后，喟然叹息，所以被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">拘</span>禁于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">牖里</span>的仓库<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百天（时长）</span>，想要害死他。为何同样称王，最终却落得<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">脯醢</span>之地？<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span>前往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夷维子</span>为他<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">执</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">策</span>驾车随行，对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>人说：'你们将如何招待我家的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主？'<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>人说：'我们将用十<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">太牢</span>招待你的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主。'<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夷维子</span>说：'你们从哪里<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>用这等<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼</span>来招待我家君主？他是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">巡狩</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>离开宫室，交出锁钥<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">筦籥</span>，敛衣执<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">机</span>席，在堂下察看膳食，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>吃完饭，才退下听政。'<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>人扔掉他们的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">籥</span>，结果没能入鲁。未得入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国，将要到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>，向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span>国借道。当时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>逝世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐湣王\">湣王（齐湣王）</span>想入境吊唁，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夷维子</span>对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span>国嗣子说：'<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>吊唁，主人必将把棺椁掉向相反方向，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南方</span>设北向座，然后<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>南面而吊。'<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span>国的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>说：'一定要这样的话，我们宁愿伏<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>而死。'所以终不敢入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐湣王\">湣王（齐湣王）</span>活着时不能事奉养他，死时不能赠送赙襚，但还想在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>之地施行<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>之<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>终究不接纳。现在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>是<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>也是<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之国。都据<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">之国</span>，各有称王之名，看到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>一次<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">胜</span>，就要奉他为帝，这是使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三晋</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>不如<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>的仆妾。况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>称帝之后将无止境，还将更换<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>。他将剥夺他所不满意的人，授予他所欣赏的人，剥夺他所憎恶的人，授予他所宠爱的人。他又将让他的子女和谗佞的姬妾成为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妃</span>妾，处于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>宫。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁王</span>怎能安然无事？而将军又怎能得到以往的宠信？\""
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "8.1": {
      "title": "新垣衍再拜谢",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">新垣衍</span>起身，再拜谢说： \"开始我以为先生是庸人，我<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">今日</span>才知道先生是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人。我请求退下，不敢再说帝<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的话。\""
    },
    "8.2": {
      "title": "秦将却军五十里",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将听说此事，为此退兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五十里</span>。"
    },
    "8.3": {
      "title": "信陵君救赵",
      "text": "适逢<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：信陵君\">魏公子（信陵君）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>夺取<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>的军队来救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军于是引兵离去。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "9.1": {
      "title": "平原君欲封鲁连",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>想要<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>再三辞让，终不肯接受。"
    },
    "9.2": {
      "title": "平原君千金寿",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>于是摆酒，酒酣时起身上前，以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>祝寿。"
    },
    "9.3": {
      "title": "鲁连笑言高节",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>笑着说： \"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>所以可贵，在于为人排忧解难、解纷乱而不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>报酬。若有<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>报酬，那是商贾之事，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">连（鲁仲连）</span>不忍心做。\""
    },
    "9.4": {
      "title": "鲁连辞平原君",
      "text": "于是辞别<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>而去，终身不再相见。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "10.1": {
      "title": "燕将守聊城",
      "text": "此后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十多年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>将<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">聊城</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">聊城</span>人有诽谤他于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国的，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>将害怕被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>，因而占据<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">聊城</span>，不敢回国。"
    },
    "10.2": {
      "title": "田单攻聊城不下",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田单</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">聊城</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒死伤众多而<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">聊城</span>攻不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span>。"
    },
    "10.3": {
      "title": "鲁连射书城中",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>就写了一封<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>信，系在<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">矢</span>上射入城中，送给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>将。"
    },
    "10.4": {
      "title": "书曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>信说："
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "鲁连书谏（第一段）",
      "text": "我听说，智者不违背时机而舍弃利益，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">勇士</span>不回避死亡而毁灭名声，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">忠臣</span>不先顾自身而后顾<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主。现在您行一时之愤怒，不顾<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕王</span>没有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子，这不是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">忠</span>；<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>身而失<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">聊城</span>，而威名不<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span>立于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国，这不是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">勇</span>；功<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>名灭，后世无人称颂，这不是智。这三样，世主不视他为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>不载他的事迹，所以智者不重犯谋划，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">勇士</span>不怯于死。如今死生荣辱、<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贵</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贱</span>尊卑，此时不再到来，希望您仔细思量而不要与俗人相同。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "鲁连书谏（第二段）",
      "text": "况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平陆</span>，而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国无南面用兵之心，以为失去<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>的损害小，不如得<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济北</span>之利大，所以决意处理。现在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>人派兵南<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">下</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>不敢东进；连衡<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>之势已成，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国形势危急；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国放弃<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>，断绝右境，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济北</span>，还是会这样做。况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>必定要在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">聊城</span>决战，您不要再作他想。现在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>都从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>撤退，而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>的救兵不至。以全<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>之兵，无<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的顾虑，与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">聊城</span>共持久到整年的疲敝，那么<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>可以预见您无法取胜。而且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国大乱，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>失策，上下迷惑，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗腹</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十万之众</span>五次在外面败北，以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之国被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>困，国土削减，君主困穷，为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>所讥笑。国家残破祸患多，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众没有归心之处。如今您又以疲敝的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名·规范：聊城\">聊（聊城）</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>抵抗全<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>之兵，这是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">墨翟</span>式的坚守。食人炊骨，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>无反叛外逃之心，这是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙膑</span>式的治军。能够显闻于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。虽然如此，替您打算，不如保全<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲</span>回报于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲</span>完全归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕王</span>必定高兴；身体完好归国，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>像见到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>一样迎接，亲朋好友扬臂争论传颂于世，功业得以彰明。上辅孤主以制<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>，下养<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>以资助说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，矫正国政改革风俗，功名可立。或者抛弃<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>而超脱世俗，东游<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>呢？割地定封，富比<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>，世代称孤，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>长存，这又是一计。这两种谋划，都能显扬名声丰厚实利，希望您仔细思量并慎重选择其一。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "鲁连书谏（第三段，管仲曹刿之例）",
      "text": "况且我听说，计较小节的人不能成就荣名，厌恶小耻的人不能立大功。从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：管仲\">管夷吾（管仲）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">射</span>中<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">桓公（齐桓公）</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钩</span>，是篡逆；遗弃<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公子纠\">纠（公子纠）</span>不殉死，是怯懦；被<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">桎梏</span>束缚，是羞辱。有这三种行为的人，世主不视为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，乡里不与之交往。若使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：管仲\">管子（管仲）</span>被幽<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span>不出，身死而不返<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，那也名不免为耻辱贱行。奴仆也羞与他同名，何况世俗呢！所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：管仲\">管子（管仲）</span>不以身在縲绁之中为耻，却以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>不治为耻；不以不为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公子纠\">纠（公子纠）</span>殉死为耻，却以威名不<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span>立于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>为耻，所以他兼有三种过失而成为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五霸</span>之首，名高<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>而光照邻国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹沫\">曹子（曹沫）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>，三<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>三败，丧失土地<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百里</span>。若使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹沫\">曹子（曹沫）</span>不顾后果，议论不回头，刎颈而死，那也名不免为<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>军擒<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹沫\">曹子（曹沫）</span>抛弃三次战败之耻，退而与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>谋划。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">桓公（齐桓公）</span>朝见<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，会合<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹沫\">曹子（曹沫）</span>以一<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>之任，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">枝</span>挺<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">桓公（齐桓公）</span>之心于坛坫之上，面不改色，辞气不乱，三次战败所丢失的土地一朝收复，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>震动，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>惊骇，威名加于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>。像这两位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，并非不能成就小廉而行小节，但他们认为<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>身亡躯，断绝后世，功名不立，不是明智。所以去除愤怒之怨，立下终身之名；抛弃一时之节，奠定累世之功。因此功业与<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">三王</span>争流，而名与天地同寿。希望您选择其一而行之。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "燕将自杀聊城屠",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>将见到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>信，哭了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三天（时长）</span>，犹豫不能自决。 想归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，已有嫌隙，怕被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>；想<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">降</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，所<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>虏的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人很多，怕投降后受辱。 喟然叹息说： \"与其让人杀我，不如自杀。\" 于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">聊城</span>大乱，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田单</span>于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">屠</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">聊城</span>。回去后提到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>，想给他加爵。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逃</span>隐于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>上，说： \"我与其<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">富贵</span>而屈服于人，宁愿<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贫贱</span>而轻视世俗、任性自由。\""
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "邹阳入狱上书",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邹阳</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国人。游历于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>，与原<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄忌</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫子</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮阴</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">枚生</span>之辈交往。他上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>而与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羊胜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙诡</span>之间周旋。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：羊胜\">胜（羊胜）</span>等人嫉妒<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邹阳</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁孝王</span>面前说他坏话。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>发怒，把他交给官吏，想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邹阳</span>客游在外，因谗言被擒，担心死后蒙受罪名，于是从狱中上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>说："
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "荆轲卫先生之例",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">忠</span>无不报，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span>不受疑，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>曾认为是这样，只不过虚话罢了。从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荆轲</span>仰慕<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕太子丹\">丹（燕太子丹）</span>的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">义</span>，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">白虹贯日</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>仍旧畏疑他；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫先生</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>谋划<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>的战事，<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">太白蚀昴</span>的天象出现，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>却怀疑他。至诚感动<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">天地</span>而<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span>不能让两位君主明白，难道不可悲吗！现在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>尽<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">忠</span>竭<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">诚</span>，毕议愿知，左右不明察，卒被吏讯审，为世所疑，这是使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荆轲</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫先生</span>再生，而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>依然不觉悟。希望大王仔细思考。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "卞和李斯之例",
      "text": "从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卞和</span>献宝，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚王</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">刖</span>他；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>竭<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">忠</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>用<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">极刑</span>。所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">箕子</span>假装发狂，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">接舆</span>避世，害怕遭受这种祸患。希望大王仔细思考<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卞和</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>的本意，不要像<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚王</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>那样听信谗言，不要使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">箕子</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">接舆</span>所讥笑。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">比干</span>被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">剖</span>心，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">鸱夷</span>装尸投入江中，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>起初不<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span>，现在才知道。希望大王仔细思考，稍加怜悯。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "王奢樊於期等相知之例",
      "text": "谚语说：\"有<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">白头如新，倾盖如故</span>。\" 为什么？是知与不知的缘故。所以从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊於期</span>逃离<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>投奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，借他的首级来成就<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荆轲</span>报<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕太子丹\">丹（燕太子丹）</span>之仇的事；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王奢</span>离开<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，登城自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">刭</span>以退<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>兵而保存<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王奢</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊於期</span>并非与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>是新交而与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>是旧交，他们之所以离开两国而为两位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主而死，是因为行事合于志向，仰慕<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">义</span>无穷。所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏秦</span>不被<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>所<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span>，却为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国作尾生式的守信之臣；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白圭</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>败失去<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六城</span>，为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>。为什么？是因为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">诚</span>有相知。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏秦</span>任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>相，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>人在王面前说他坏话，王按<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>而怒，还以珍馐款待他；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白圭</span>显扬于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>人在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏文侯</span>面前说他坏话，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏文侯\">文侯（魏文侯）</span>赐他<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">夜光之璧</span>。为什么？两位君主和两位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子，剖心坼肝相<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span>，岂会因浮言移转！"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "贤士遭嫉之例",
      "text": "所以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>人无论美丑，入宫就受嫉妒；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人无论贤与不肖，入朝就受嫉妒。从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">司马喜</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>被髌足之刑，最终做了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>的相；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范睢</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>被折胁断齿，最终做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">应侯</span>。这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，都是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span>赖必然的谋划，抛弃朋党的私情，挟持孤独的处境，所以不能自免于嫉妒之人。因此<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申徒狄</span>自沉于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">徐衍</span>负石入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>。他们不被世所容，但<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">义</span>不苟且<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>利，不在朝廷结党，以动摇<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">主上</span>之心。所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">百里奚</span>乞食于路，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦缪公\">缪公（秦缪公）</span>把政事交给他；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甯戚</span>在<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>下<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">饭</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">桓公（齐桓公）</span>把国政交给他。这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，难道是借宦于朝，假誉于左右，然后二主才任用他们的吗？是心心相感，行合志同，亲密胜过胶漆，就是兄<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>也难以离间，岂会被众口所迷惑？所以偏听生奸，独任成乱。从前<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>听<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季孙</span>的话而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子罕</span>的计谋而<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">墨翟</span>。凭<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孔子\">孔（孔子）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：墨翟\">墨（墨翟）</span>的辩才，都不能自免于谗谀，而两国因此<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">危</span>。为什么？众口铄金，积毁销骨啊。所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>用<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">戎</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">由余</span>而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">霸</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>用<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：越人蒙\">蒙（越人蒙）</span>而强于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐威王\">威（齐威王）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐宣王\">宣（齐宣王）</span>。这两国，难道是拘于世俗，牵于流言，听从阿偏之辞吗？公听并观，流芳当世。所以意合则<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>也如兄<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">由余</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：越人蒙\">蒙（越人蒙）</span>就是这样；不合，则骨肉被驱逐也不收，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：丹朱\">硃（丹朱）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：舜弟象\">象（舜弟象）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：管叔\">管（管叔）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：蔡叔\">蔡（蔡叔）</span>就是这样。现在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人主</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">诚</span>若能用<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">义</span>，不学<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>偏听，那么<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五伯</span>不足称，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">三王</span>易为啊。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "圣王觉寤之例",
      "text": "所以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣王</span>觉悟，抛弃<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>之心，不悦于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田常</span>的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤</span>；<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">比干</span>的后人，修孕妇的墓，所以功业重新成就于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。为什么？是因为向善无厌。那<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋文公</span>亲近他的仇人，强盛地<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">霸</span>于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐桓公</span>用他的仇人，一匡<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。为什么？仁慈<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁</span>德殷勤，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">诚</span>加于心，不能用虚辞来借托。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "秦用商鞅越用大夫种之例",
      "text": "至于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商鞅</span>之法，东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">弱</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，兵强<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，而最终<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">车裂</span>了他；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>的谋略，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">禽</span>强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">霸</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>，而最终<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>其身。所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙叔敖</span>三次辞相而不悔，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">於陵子仲</span>辞<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三公</span>而为人浇园。现在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人主</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">诚</span>能去掉骄泬之心，怀可报之意，披心腹，见情素，堕肝胆，施<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>厚，终与之共穷达，不吝惜<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，那么<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狗</span>可使它对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>吠叫，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蹠</span>的门客可使他去<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：许由\">由（许由）</span>；何况凭借<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之权，借<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣王</span>之资呢？这样，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荆轲</span>连累七<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">要离</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">烧</span>死妻子，就算不得什么了！"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "明月夜光之喻",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">明月之珠</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">夜光之璧</span>，在暗中向人投于道路之上，人们无不按<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>斜视的。为什么？因为无端而至于前。盘结的树<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">木</span>根柢，盘曲离奇，却能成为<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之主的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">器</span>。为什么？因为左右先为它修饰称扬。所以无端而至前，即使拿出<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">随侯之珠</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">夜光之璧</span>，还会结怨而不被视为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>。所以有人先引介，则以枯<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">木</span>朽株建功也会不被遗忘。现在<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">布衣</span>穷居之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，身处<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贫贱</span>，虽然拥有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>之术，挟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伊尹\">伊（伊尹）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：管仲\">管（管仲）</span>之辩，怀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">龙逢</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">比干</span>之志，想尽<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">忠</span>于当世之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，但平素没有根柢的修饰，虽然竭尽精思，想开<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">忠</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span>之言，辅助<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人主</span>之治，那么<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人主</span>必有按<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>斜视的反应，这就使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">布衣</span>不能为枯<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">木</span>朽株之资。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "圣王独观昭旷之道",
      "text": "所以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣王</span>制世御俗，独自主宰于陶钧之上，而不被卑乱的言论所牵制，不被众多的口舌所夺取。所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>任用<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中庶子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙嘉</span>之言，因而<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荆轲</span>的话，而<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">匕首</span>得以暗中发作；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周文王</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泾水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭水</span>打猎，载<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕尚</span>归来，而统治<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span>左右而遭<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>用乌合之众而王。为什么？因为能超越拘束的言论，驰骋域外的议论，独自观察于昭旷的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道</span>。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "士与牛骥同皁之叹",
      "text": "现在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人主</span>沉溺于谄谀之辞，被后宫女人之制所牵制，使不羁的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人与<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">骥</span>同槽，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲍焦</span>所以愤世而不留恋<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">富</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贵</span>之乐的原因。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "盛饰入朝不污义",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说盛装<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">入</span>朝的人不因利益玷污<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">义</span>，砥砺名声的人不因欲望损害品行，所以县名叫<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">胜母</span>而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曾子</span>不进入，邑号<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">朝歌</span>而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">墨子</span>调回<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>。现在想让<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>寥廓的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，摄于威重的权势，屈主于位势的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贵</span>显，所以回面污行去事奉谄谀之人以求接近左右，那么<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人就伏死在山穴岩洞中，岂肯有尽<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">忠</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">信</span>而趋赴阙下的？"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "得释为上客",
      "text": "<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>信上奏<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁孝王</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：梁孝王\">孝王（梁孝王）</span>派人把他放出来，最终做了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上客</span>。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>的旨意虽然不完全合于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">大义</span>，然而我赞赏他以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">布衣</span>之身，豁达放任，不屈服于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，纵论于当世，挫折了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卿相</span>之权。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邹阳</span>言辞虽然不够谦逊，然而他比物连类，有令人悲叹之处，也可说是抗直不屈了，我因此把他附于<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">列传</span>。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲁仲连\">鲁连（鲁仲连）</span>是达<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，有高才远见。 解除危难解开纷争，辞禄位而任放心志。 挫折<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>将的辩辞，使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>军沮丧士气。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：邹阳\">邹子（邹阳）</span>遭受谗言，在狱吏前被诋毁。 慷慨献计陈说，当时之王倚重他。"
    }
  }
}